OL,3,CWorld's happiest country tops list for
OL,4,Ceighth year - but where does UK rank?
OL,6,FThe UK has sunk lower on the World
OL,7,FHappiness Report, as ITV News' Rhys
OL,8,FWilliams reports
OL,10,FFinland has been named the world's
OL,11,Fhappiest country for the eighth year
OL,12,Fin a row, but the outlook in other
OL,13,Fparts of Europe was not quite so sunny.
OL,15,FThis year's World Happiness Report saw
OL,16,Fthe UK's happiness sink to its lowest
OL,17,Flevel since 2017, coming in at number
OL,18,F23 on the list. And after dropping out
OL,19,Fof the top 20 for the first time last
OL,20,Fyear, the US ranked even further
OL,21,Fbehind at number 24.
