OL,3,CWorld's happiest country tops list for
OL,4,Ceighth year - but where does UK rank?
OL,6,FThe authors of the report say that
OL,7,Fdeclining happiness and social trust
OL,8,Fin the US, UK, and other parts of
OL,9,FEurope have contributed significantly
OL,10,Fto the rise of political polarisation
OL,11,Fand votes against "the system".
OL,13,FThe report draws on polling data from
OL,14,Fpeople in more than 140 countries. The
OL,15,Fcountries are ranked on happiness
OL,16,Fbased on their average life
OL,17,Fevaluations over the three preceding
OL,18,Fyears - in this case, 2022-2024.
