OL,3,CWorld's happiest country tops list for
OL,4,Ceighth year - but where does UK rank?
OL,6,FThe survey asks each participant to
OL,7,Fscore their life as a whole and
OL,8,Frankings are based on those life
OL,9,Fevaluations, GDP per capita, social
OL,10,Fsupport, healthy life expectancy,
OL,11,Ffreedom, generosity, and perceptions
OL,12,Fof corruption.
OL,14,FNordic countries typically top those
OL,15,Flists, with 2025 proving no exception.
OL,16,FFinland, Denmark, Iceland and Sweden
OL,17,Fremain the top four countries as they
OL,18,Fdid in 2024, with Norway coming
OL,19,Fseventh.
