OL,3,CWorld's happiest country tops list for
OL,4,Ceighth year - but where does UK rank?
OL,6,F"Nordic countries like Finland
OL,7,Fcontinue to benefit from universally
OL,8,Favailable and high-quality health,
OL,9,Feducation and social support systems.
OL,10,FInequality of wellbeing is also low,"
OL,11,Fsaid Ilana Ron-Levey, managing
OL,12,Fdirector at Gallup, who organised the
OL,13,Fsurveys.
OL,15,FExperts also point to a friendly and
OL,16,Ftrusting social culture, and a less
OL,17,Fmaterialistic mindset, as being
OL,18,Fimportant to Finland's happiness.
