OL,3,CWorld's happiest country tops list for
OL,4,Ceighth year - but where does UK rank?
OL,6,FTwo Latin American countries have also
OL,7,Fentered the top 10 for the first time,
OL,8,Fwith Costa Rica coming sixth, and
OL,9,FMexico in tenth place.
OL,11,FBoth countries' residents have "strong
OL,12,Fsupport networks and strong
OL,13,Fperceptions about the direction of
OL,14,Ftheir economy and confidence in
OL,15,Fleaders and institutions," Ron-Levey
OL,16,Fsaid.
