OL,3,CWorld's happiest country tops list for
OL,4,Ceighth year - but where does UK rank?
OL,6,FThe report highlights the importance
OL,7,Fof caring and sharing with others for
OL,8,Fpeople's happiness. The poll found
OL,9,Fthat those who gave money to charity,
OL,10,Fvolunteered, and helped strangers came
OL,11,Fout happier, making their societies
OL,12,Fhappier as a result.
OL,14,FThe extent to which individuals help
OL,15,Feach other in societies, and expect
OL,16,Fothers to help them, is referred to in
OL,17,Fthe report as benevolence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
