OL,3,CWorld's happiest country tops list for
OL,4,Ceighth year - but where does UK rank?
OL,6,FThe report states that the degree of
OL,7,Fbenevolence in a country has a
OL,8,Fprofound impact on its politics, with
OL,9,Fpopulism largely due to unhappiness.
OL,10,FThe authors argue that the decline in
OL,11,Flife satisfaction explains the overall
OL,12,Frise in populist votes.
OL,14,FAmong unhappy people attracted to the
OL,15,Fextremes of the political spectrum,
OL,16,Fthose who do not have trust in others
OL,17,Fare more often found on the far right,
OL,18,Fwhereas high-trust people are more
OL,19,Finclined to vote for the far left.
